The statement expresses condolences for the passing of Sheldon Adelson, describing him as a giant and a friend. Adelson is praised for embodying the American dream, being a generous philanthropist, and changing many lives as a businessman. His belief in America and the alliance with Israel is highlighted, particularly the move of the US Embassy to Jerusalem. Adelson is compared to a leader and a great man in Israel, and his legacy is said to inspire future generations. The statement concludes with a prayer for comfort to his wife, children, and grandchildren.